_xResult.title: Tired of Love Jacket
_xResult.shortdesc: Custom made red jacket with pockets
_xResult.longdesc:
This custom made cashmere jacket features a cape-like collar, two side pockets and a midi length that will keep you comfortable and warm all winter long. This jacket is super soft and made of pure cashmere with no lining, making it a true treat to wear. If you’ve never had a jacket or coat custom made to your measurements, you’ll love the feeling of knowing its made just for you and fits you perfectly!

 

Have fun with EUG's custom made designer clothing! For custom made requests regarding sizing, let the designer know using the button below.
